These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
City: liverpool, san-francisco, rome, paris, hamburg, prague, boston
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, february, september, april, october, december, november
The people have 7 different jobs:  security-guard, musician, paramedic, writer, chef, videographer, accountant
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the writer is on the far right##1
 2. the chef is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the paramedic##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is the paramedic##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person traveling to rome is in the middle##1
11. the security-guard is the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
14. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
16. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
17. the videographer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
18. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
19. the accountant is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| City      | san-francisco  | prague        | hamburg | rome      | paris     | liverpool      | boston     |
| Birthday   | february | april         | november   | august | december    | october | september |
| Job         | paramedic | chef | security-guard | musician | accountant  | videographer  | writer    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

