 8. the person playing bridge is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
10. the person playing chess is between the person playing poker and the person watching epic movies##2
11. the person playing domino is the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person watching epic movies and the person playing scrabble##2
14. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
18. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
